1&amp;pmid=3964962">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">17.</div><div id="REF17" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Yeo CJ, Barry MK, Sauter PK, et al. <i>Erythromycin accelerates gastric emptying after pancreaticoduodenectomy: a prospective, randomized placebo-controlled trial.</i> <em>Ann Surg</em> 1993; 218:229-238.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1097/00000658-199309000-00002">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/8103982/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Erythromycin+accelerates+gastric+emptying+after+pancreaticoduodenectomy%3A+a+prospective%2C+randomized+placebo-controlled+trial.&amp;publication_year=1993&amp;pages=229&amp;doi=10.1097%2F00000658-199309000-00002&amp;pmid=8103982">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">18.</div><div id="REF18" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Yeo CJ. <i>Management of complications following pancreaticoduodenectomy.</i> <em>Surg Clin North Am</em> 1995; 75:913-924.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/S0039-6109(16)46736-8">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/7660254/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Management+of+complications+following+pancreaticoduodenectomy.&amp;publication_year=1995&amp;pages=913&amp;doi=10.1016%2FS0039-6109%2816%2946736-8&amp;pmid=7660254">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">19.</div><div id="REF19" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="cit